    "# Group Tasks, Week 2\n",
    "\n",
    "In [Lecture 02](https://colab.research.google.com/github/fmfi-compbio/viz//blob/master/notebooks/L02_Processing_Pandas.ipynb), we processed data from a table containing various country statistics from the UN. In these tasks, you will work with the same table and do a slight variation of the analysis from the lecture. We recommend for each task below finding similar code in the lecture and adapting it. \n",
    "\n",
    "* Please follow the guidelines for [submitting notebooks](https://fmfi-compbio.github.io/viz/Tutorial1.html\\#pokyny-k-zadaniam) and for [working in teams](https://fmfi-compbio.github.io/viz/Groups.html). \n",
    "* Do not forget to **switch off AI assistants** in Colab `Menu->Tools->Settings->AI Assistance`. You may switch it on when working on bonus B.\n",
    "* Use only the four libraries imported below. \n",
    "* To process data, use **Pandas functions rather than loops or list comprehension**.\n",
    "\n",
   ]
  },
